By Steve Agbota THE Chief Executive Officer of DO.II Designs Limited, Ifeyinwa Ighodalo, has said that power and infrastructure pose greatest challenge to the development of interior design sector in the country. But inspite of the challenges facing the sector, she said DO.II has been providing affordable solutions with excellent global standards tailored to the uniqueness of commercial and private consumers in the country. Speaking at a media parley in Lagos, Ighodalo said the company was planning to expand its operation by opening more outlets in Lagos and Abuja aloneside other densely populated areas in order to make the products available and affordable without losing quality. 